             was indicted for <rs id="t18200217-33-off191" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200217-33-off191" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200217-33-off191" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200217-33-cd192" type="crimeDate">7th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200217-33-off191 t18200217-33-cd192"></join>, one handkerchief, value 5 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200217-33-victim469" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Ryder
                        <interp inst="t18200217-33-victim469" type="surname" value="Ryder"></interp>
